articles.title: PM Modi 'chosen by God': American singer Mary Millben after Lok Sabha exit polls results | Mint - Mint
articles.description: According to all exit polls, the BJP-led National Democratic Alliance will cross 350-plus mark in the Lok Sabha Elections, whose official counting will take place on 4 June.
articles.content: Amid the exit polls favouring Prime Minister Narendra Modi's Bharatiya Janata Party returning to power for third time, American singer and actress Mary Millben on 2 June referred PM Modi as the best … [+2304 chars]
